										<content:encoded><![CDATA[<p>Inflatable lifejacket designed for use in open sea and extreme weather conditions, even when worn over heavy and waterproof clothing. Ideal for yachts, it is particularly suited for professional use on bulk carriers, liquid cargo vessels and offshore units, as well as in the cruise sector for crews, emergency teams, safety personnel and deck operations. The ergonomic design ensures freedom of movement during all operational activities, both on board and in the water.</p>
<h3>FEATURES</h3>
<ul class="top-features">
<li>Actual Buoyancy 295N</li>
<li>CO2 Cylinder Size 2 x 60gr</li>
<li>Crotch Strap</li>
<li>Status Indicator Window</li>
</ul>
